{"tid":81230,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有圖整合 買演唱會飛受騙，各位小心！！","createTime":"2017-01-15T07:21:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-15T07:21:42.000Z","uid":5198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b8431f01daa977c86bf28a1edd6c463518ba3da7","tid":81230,"uid":5198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T07:21:42.000Z","msg":"圖已順序<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話說係10月個陣，我娘親話想睇歌神演唱會<br />\n但人地個陣公售都完左，邊度同你搵張飛比你<br />\n但身為孝子嘅我，梗係唔想娘親失望<br />\n咪上網睇下有冇人放飛啦，竟然比係一個放飛網度見到有人用正價980放4張飛，我梗係狗衝啦<br />\n<br />\n我就wtsapp條仆街，問係咪有飛放<br />\n佢話有仲叫我入住半數比佢先，咁我就入左半數比佢，過幾日仲叫我入埋尾數比佢<br />\n我就覺得奇怪，就話拎飛個陣先比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n約佢交收，初頭就約佢下星期交收，到個日，佢就話票房未有飛比佢要改日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢之後約過時間幾次，佢都話未收到飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我開始質問佢啲飛點，佢就話可以寄比我，我心諗仲好唔洗特登出去拎，之後成個月我日日睇信箱，望穿秋水都見唔到啲飛。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去到演唱會前一個星期，我就催佢啦，佢就話過幾日有，叫我面交，我個心已經問候佢娘親好多次，最後約好左日子時間之後。去到演唱會前一日，屌佢條仆街話提議回水比我，仲話可以比張唔知乜撚pass我入去睇，我就叫佢比反錢我算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住佢話要等公司定邊撚度回水比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就話點解初頭過錢就過私人戶口，依家就要等唔知邊度比反先有，同埋咁撚大個人，出住千幾蚊有幾難，我就同佢講你比個日子我，再唔回就報警放上網，最後梗係冇比度，依家連機都唔應啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然話千幾蚊當豪比狗，但為免各位巴絲受騙，提醒大家，小心此人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:警已報。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZKyjqLr5oREUuwPwdmYdNvDPmNT5L3c1nigutygV7bQm?filename=a52jwyE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa52jwyE.jpg&h=3dbbc57a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSHoaMvrzaB1YDxbpD2QqPifE5THGvHhFt12XGPGYS1z6?filename=k675r49.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk675r49.jpg&h=13a88616&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/15/151347_3ac57ceb18a350144a6352ec2dbaf740.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F15%2F151347_3ac57ceb18a350144a6352ec2dbaf740.jpg&h=7c3a989a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcLby5eLH1RBkeFpJdwkJSWpm4NChsX8DFaX1qqHgoswM?filename=5OZ81t8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5OZ81t8.jpg&h=d885f1bc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/15/151347_21fd04d3a9d4744f4c65f81443a87f37.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F15%2F151347_21fd04d3a9d4744f4c65f81443a87f37.jpg&h=05f3045a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/15/151443_22551df9519e77e1878f6a499efb7fb1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F15%2F151443_22551df9519e77e1878f6a499efb7fb1.jpg&h=e7650031&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVUcnqagbRPQL1utHkgbSfNQAYTNBaKFZdnriEVNHF2mD?filename=3vzLK3m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3vzLK3m.jpg&h=b03f2179&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/15/151443_642ff3ea72999fd14dd6e14d34bd2712.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F15%2F151443_642ff3ea72999fd14dd6e14d34bd2712.jpg&h=e2f9af21&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/15/151444_642ff3ea72999fd14dd6e14d34bd2712.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F15%2F151444_642ff3ea72999fd14dd6e14d34bd2712.jpg&h=170c5685&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYxoU6hnzWstx5WXNq7bu35mSRGdKr9i4XhTxBc8nocar?filename=xKz0963.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxKz0963.jpg&h=f254511e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSrXCsxk7vE4hMHXrMHbBfPPgpXdNHXMn8fYoyXMswQgA?filename=TQoxdyD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTQoxdyD.jpg&h=88f943f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQudMHiAoejnxd4VyBJswabRvbPPXiez5qQpLBqKjuUqY?filename=96U4a0b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F96U4a0b.jpg&h=49132006&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVW9m25xaJkLRMAWnaWsnka2KBhyA3WqjDEcdew2gpT2N?filename=8xQ3930.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8xQ3930.jpg&h=3d077c55&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmes4Wkiu7RY8eJLQPvHZ2e3mDrndRmHDnkTcqWm32pxa2?filename=33s8ati.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F33s8ati.jpg&h=a509eb0c&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}